com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.mrcm

Interface ConstraintBase

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, ConceptModelComponent, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AttributeConstraint
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AttributeConstraintImpl, ConstraintBaseImpl

    public interface ConstraintBase
extends ConceptModelComponent
    A representation of the model object 'Constraint Base'. Abstract base class for concept model constraints.

    The following features are supported:

    • Strength
    • Validation Message
    • Description

    See Also:
    MrcmPackage.getConstraintBase()
